trans-unit.source: Computes aggregates over a sequence of Int32 values.
Finds the average of a sequence of Int32 values.
A value of type <xref uid="langword_csharp_Int32" name="Int32" href=""></xref> that identifies a group of items to average, such as a column in a table.
Returns the average result of a sequence of Int32 values.
An <xref uid="langword_csharp_Int32" name="Int32" href=""></xref> value that contains the average result of a sequence of <xref uid="langword_csharp_Int32" name="Int32" href=""></xref> values.
Initializes a sequence of <xref uid="langword_csharp_Int32" name="Int32" href=""></xref> values.
Returns a Boolean value that indicates if the sequence is empty.
<xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the sequence is empty, otherwise returns <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
Assigns the value parameter to the existing result if the value parameter is greater than the existing result.
A value of type <xref uid="langword_csharp_Int32" name="Int32" href=""></xref>.
Returns the largest value in a sequence of <xref uid="langword_csharp_Int32" name="Int32" href=""></xref> values.
An <xref uid="langword_csharp_Int32" name="Int32" href=""></xref> value that contains the maximum value in a sequence of <xref uid="langword_csharp_Int32" name="Int32" href=""></xref> values.
Assigns the value parameter to the existing result if the value parameter is less than the existing result.
A value of type <xref uid="langword_csharp_Int32" name="Int32" href=""></xref>
Returns the smallest value in a sequence of Int32 values.
An <xref uid="langword_csharp_Int32" name="Int32" href=""></xref> value that contains the minimum value in a sequence of <xref uid="langword_csharp_Int32" name="Int32" href=""></xref> values.
Adds an <xref uid="langword_csharp_Int32" name="Int32" href=""></xref> value to the existing result.
A value of type <xref uid="langword_csharp_Int32" name="Int32" href=""></xref>.
Returns the sum of a sequence of Int32 values.
An <xref uid="langword_csharp_Int32" name="Int32" href=""></xref> value that contains the sum of a sequence of <xref uid="langword_csharp_Int32" name="Int32" href=""></xref> values.
